People stay at home to avoid the hot sun. All around is the sound of cicadas. At this time, flies are the most boring creature. They fly here and there and tread on food and plates. Itâs so dirty. Flies are nice dinner for spider. Once the game starts, there are many flies and a big spider in the screen. Control the Frog clicking on it and dragging backwards to make a perfect angle to bite a fly. Watch out for the swatter. It is your greatest enemy. Kill a fly and you will get five points. For the big fly, you get ten points. Good luck!Frog game, bite fly, jumping, fun, cool
